snippet.title: The World & Plot / Aggregate Core Devlog 1
snippet.description:
Hey everyone, we're back with another devlog addressing the world, plot and player character of our game! Thank you to everyone for all the interest from the previous devlog and we hope this video helps clear the story up. Also, if anyone is interested in what our process for creating and implementing 3d characters into our game looks like, let us know!

Wishlist on Steam!
